OBJECT Report 78778 PCS TOPsheet
{
  OBJECT-PROPERTIES
  {
    Date=;
    Time=;
    Version List=4PS9.00.BK.OK;
  }
  PROPERTIES
  {
  }
  DATASET
  {
    { 8019;    ;DataItem;                    ;
               DataItemTable=Table11072003;
               DataItemTableView=SORTING(No.);
               OnPreDataItem=VAR
                               TempDate@1000000000 : Date;
                               AccPeriod@1000000001 : Record 50;
                             BEGIN
                               IF Job.GETFILTER("Cumulation Filter") = '' THEN
                                 SETFILTER("Period Filter", PeriodFilterTxt);
                               IF Job.GETFILTER("Cumulation Filter") = '' THEN
                                 SETFILTER("Cumulation Filter", CumulationFilterTxt)
                               ELSE BEGIN
                                 CumulationFilterTxt := Job.GETFILTER("Cumulation Filter");
                                 EVALUATE(TempDate, COPYSTR(Job.GETFILTER("Cumulation Filter"), 3, 8));
                                 DatFilterEnd := TempDate;
                                 AccPeriod.SETFILTER("Starting Date",'<%1', TempDate);
                                 IF AccPeriod.FINDLAST THEN
                                   DatFilterStart := (AccPeriod."Starting Date");
                                 PeriodFilterTxt := STRSUBSTNO('%1 %2', DatFilterStart, CumulationFilterTxt);
                                 SETFILTER("Period Filter", PeriodFilterTxt);
                                 SETFILTER("Cumulation Filter", CumulationFilterTxt);
                               END;

                               IF Job.GETFILTER("Period Filter") = '' THEN
                                 SETFILTER("Period Filter", PeriodFilterTxt);
                               IF Job.GETFILTER("Cumulation Filter") = '' THEN
                                 SETFILTER("Cumulation Filter", CumulationFilterTxt)
                               ELSE
                                 PeriodFilterTxt := Job.GETFILTER("Period Filter");

                               //SearchPeriod.FindPeriod(DatFilterStart,DatFilterEnd,CumulationFilterTxt,PeriodFilterTxt,PeriodType::"Accounting Period",'');
                               DPA_SetFilters(CurrReport.OBJECTID(FALSE)); //4PS.n
                               PeriodType := PeriodType::"Accounting Period";
                             END;

               OnAfterGetRecord=VAR
                                  Language@1000000000 : Record 8;
                                BEGIN
                                  CurrReport.LANGUAGE := Language.GetLanguageID("Language Code");

                                  LineNumber := 0;
                                  LineNumberCostType := 0;
                                  IF "Single/Main/Sub Project" <> Job."Single/Main/Sub Project"::"Main Project" THEN
                                    SETFILTER("Project Filter", "No.");
                                  CALCFIELDS("Project Contract Amount","Contract Amount","Extension Contract Amount",Budget,"Actual Costs");
                                  CALCFIELDS("Budget Hours (Entire Project)","Actual Hours","Open Hours");

                                  ClearVarJob;
                                  CreateCtrlCostType.RUN(Job);
                                  CreateCtrlCostObj.RUN(Job);
                                  SearchPeriods;

                                  SearchPrognosis(1,PeriodDate[1],"Single/Main/Sub Project");
                                  SearchPrognosis(2,PeriodDate[2],"Single/Main/Sub Project");
                                  SearchPrognosis(3,PeriodDate[3],"Single/Main/Sub Project");

                                  IF "Single/Main/Sub Project" = Job."Single/Main/Sub Project"::"Main Project" THEN
                                    ContractAmount := "Project Contract Amount"
                                  ELSE
                                    ContractAmount := "Contract Amount";

                                  CASE "Single/Main/Sub Project" OF
                                    "Single/Main/Sub Project"::"Main Project": ProjSrtTxt := STRSUBSTNO('%1 (incl. deelproject)',
                                      FORMAT("Single/Main/Sub Project"));
                                    "Single/Main/Sub Project"::"Sub Project": ProjSrtTxt := FORMAT("Single/Main/Sub Project");
                                    "Single/Main/Sub Project"::Single: ProjSrtTxt := FORMAT("Single/Main/Sub Project");
                                  END;


                                  IF ("Starting Date" <> 0D) AND ("Ending Date" <> 0D) THEN BEGIN
                                    ProjectDays[1] := "Ending Date" - "Starting Date";
                                    ProjectDays[2] := "Ending Date" - TODAY;
                                    IF ProjectDays[1] <> 0 THEN
                                      ProjectDays[3] := 100 - (ProjectDays[2] / ProjectDays[1] * 100);
                                  END;

                                  JobLedgEntryRec.RESET;
                                  JobLedgEntryRec.SETCURRENTKEY("Main Project No.","Job No.","Document No.","Posting Date");
                                  IF "Single/Main/Sub Project" <> "Single/Main/Sub Project"::"Main Project" THEN
                                    JobLedgEntryRec.SETFILTER("Job No.","No.");
                                  JobLedgEntryRec.SETFILTER("Main Project No.", "Main Project");
                                  JobLedgEntryRec.SETFILTER("Posting Date",GETFILTER("Cumulation Filter"));
                                  JobLedgEntryRec.SETRANGE("Entry Type",JobLedgEntryRec."Entry Type"::Sale);
                                  JobLedgEntryRec.DPA_SetFilters(CurrReport.OBJECTID(FALSE)); //**4PS.n
                                  IF JobLedgEntryRec.FINDSET THEN BEGIN
                                    REPEAT
                                      ProjInstallmentsRec.RESET;
                                      IF ProjInstallmentsRec.GET(JobLedgEntryRec."Job No.",JobLedgEntryRec.Principal,
                                                             JobLedgEntryRec."Plot No.",JobLedgEntryRec."Installment No.") THEN BEGIN
                                        IF (ProjInstallmentsRec."Extension Contract" <> '') OR (ProjInstallmentsRec.Option <> '') THEN
                                          ExtensionsInvoiced := ExtensionsInvoiced - JobLedgEntryRec."Total Price (LCY)"
                                        ELSE
                                          InstallmentsInvoiced := InstallmentsInvoiced - JobLedgEntryRec."Total Price (LCY)";
                                      END ELSE
                                        CostPlusInvoiced -= JobLedgEntryRec."Total Price (LCY)"
                                    UNTIL JobLedgEntryRec.NEXT = 0;
                                  END;

                                  ExtensionContractRec.RESET;
                                  IF "Single/Main/Sub Project" <> "Single/Main/Sub Project"::"Main Project" THEN
                                    ExtensionContractRec.SETFILTER("Project No.","No.");
                                  ExtensionContractRec.SETFILTER("Main Project No.","Main Project");
                                  ExtensionContractRec.SETFILTER("Version Date",GETFILTER("Cumulation Filter"));
                                  ExtensionContractRec.SETFILTER(Status,'<>%1',ExtensionContractRec.Status::Expired);
                                  IF ExtensionContractRec.FINDSET THEN BEGIN
                                    REPEAT
                                      IF ExtensionContractRec."Settlement Method" = ExtensionContractRec."Settlement Method"::"Fixed Price" THEN
                                        ExtensionApproved[1] :=  ExtensionApproved[1] + ExtensionContractRec."Expected Contract Amount";

                                      IF (ExtensionContractRec."Settlement Method" = ExtensionContractRec."Settlement Method"::"Cost Plus") AND
                                        (ExtensionContractRec."Contract Amount (LCY)" <> 0) THEN
                                          ExtensionApproved[2] := ExtensionContractRec."Contract Amount (LCY)";

                                      IF (ExtensionContractRec."Settlement Method" = ExtensionContractRec."Settlement Method"::"Cost Plus") AND
                                        (ExtensionContractRec."Offered Amount" <> 0) THEN
                                          ExtensionApproved[2] := ExtensionContractRec."Offered Amount";

                                      IF ((ExtensionContractRec.Status = ExtensionContractRec.Status::Order) OR
                                        (ExtensionContractRec.Status = ExtensionContractRec.Status::"Invoicing Allowed")) AND
                                          (ExtensionContractRec."Settlement Method" = ExtensionContractRec."Settlement Method"::"Fixed Price") THEN
                                            ExtensionApproved[3] :=  ExtensionApproved[3] + ExtensionContractRec."Contract Amount (LCY)";

                                      IF ((ExtensionContractRec.Status = ExtensionContractRec.Status::Order) OR
                                        (ExtensionContractRec.Status = ExtensionContractRec.Status::"Invoicing Allowed")) AND
                                          (ExtensionContractRec."Settlement Method" = ExtensionContractRec."Settlement Method"::"Cost Plus") THEN
                                            ExtensionApproved[4] :=  ExtensionApproved[4] + ExtensionContractRec."Contract Amount (LCY)";

                                      IF (ExtensionContractRec.Status = ExtensionContractRec.Status::Order) OR
                                        (ExtensionContractRec.Status = ExtensionContractRec.Status::"Invoicing Allowed") THEN BEGIN
                                          IF (ExtensionContractRec."Contract Amount (LCY)" > 0) THEN
                                            ExtensionDec[1] := ExtensionDec[1] + ExtensionContractRec."Contract Amount (LCY)"
                                          ELSE
                                            ExtensionDec[2] := ExtensionDec[2] + ExtensionContractRec."Contract Amount (LCY)";
                                      END;

                                      IF ((ExtensionContractRec.Status = ExtensionContractRec.Status::Offered) OR
                                        (ExtensionContractRec.Status = ExtensionContractRec.Status::Applied)) AND (ExtensionContractRec."Treat like Order")  THEN
                                        ExtensionLikeOrder := ExtensionLikeOrder + ExtensionContractRec."Expected Contract Amount";

                                      IF (NOT ExtensionContractRec."Treat like Order") THEN BEGIN
                                        IF ExtensionContractRec.Status = ExtensionContractRec.Status::Applied THEN
                                          ExtensionDec[3] := ExtensionDec[3] + ExtensionContractRec."Estimated Amount";
                                        IF ExtensionContractRec.Status = ExtensionContractRec.Status::Offered THEN
                                          ExtensionDec[3] := ExtensionDec[3] + ExtensionContractRec."Offered Amount";
                                      END;
                                    UNTIL ExtensionContractRec.NEXT = 0;
                                  END;

                                  ToRecSpentDec[3] := (ContractAmount + ExtensionApproved[1] + ExtensionApproved[2]) -
                                    (InstallmentsInvoiced + ExtensionsInvoiced + CostPlusInvoiced);

                                  IF (ContractAmount + ExtensionApproved[1] + ExtensionApproved[2]) <> 0 THEN
                                    ToRecSpentDec[4] := ROUND(100 * ToRecSpentDec[3] / (ContractAmount + ExtensionApproved[1] + ExtensionApproved[2]),0.1);

                                  CreateCommentLine("No.");

                                  JobLedgEntryRec.RESET;
                                  JobLedgEntryRec.SETCURRENTKEY("Main Project No.","Job No.","Document No.","Posting Date");
                                  IF "Single/Main/Sub Project" <> "Single/Main/Sub Project"::"Main Project" THEN
                                    JobLedgEntryRec.SETFILTER("Job No.","No.");
                                  JobLedgEntryRec.SETFILTER("Main Project No.", "Main Project");
                                  JobLedgEntryRec.SETFILTER("Posting Date",GETFILTER("Cumulation Filter"));
                                  JobLedgEntryRec.SETRANGE("Entry Type",JobLedgEntryRec."Entry Type"::Usage);
                                  JobLedgEntryRec.SETRANGE(Surcharge,FALSE);
                                  JobLedgEntryRec.DPA_SetFilters(CurrReport.OBJECTID(FALSE)); //**4PS.n
                                  IF JobLedgEntryRec.FINDSET THEN BEGIN
                                    REPEAT
                                      VendorEntryRec.RESET;
                                      VendorEntryRec.SETCURRENTKEY("Document No.");
                                      VendorEntryRec.SETFILTER(
                                        "Document Type",'%1|%2',VendorEntryRec."Document Type"::Invoice,VendorEntryRec."Document Type"::"Credit Memo");
                                      VendorEntryRec.SETFILTER("Document No.",JobLedgEntryRec."Document No.");
                                      VendorEntryRec.SETRANGE("Posting Date", JobLedgEntryRec."Posting Date");
                                      IF VendorEntryRec.FINDSET THEN BEGIN
                                        REPEAT
                                          VendorEntryRec.CALCFIELDS("Original Amt. (LCY)","Remaining Amt. (LCY)");
                                          PayedAmnt := VendorEntryRec."Original Amt. (LCY)" - VendorEntryRec."Remaining Amt. (LCY)";
                                          IF VendorEntryRec."Remaining Amt. (LCY)" <> 0 THEN
                                            PayedPerc := (PayedAmnt / VendorEntryRec."Original Amt. (LCY)") * 100
                                          ELSE
                                            PayedPerc := 100;
                                          VendorBalance[1] := VendorBalance[1] + (JobLedgEntryRec."Total Cost (LCY)" / 100) * PayedPerc;  //Betaalde cred
                                          VendorBalance[2] := VendorBalance[2] + ((JobLedgEntryRec."Total Cost (LCY)" * (100 - PayedPerc))) / 100;
                                        UNTIL VendorEntryRec.NEXT = 0;
                                      END;
                                    UNTIL JobLedgEntryRec.NEXT = 0;
                                  END;

                                  CLEAR(PayedAmnt);
                                  CLEAR(PayedPerc);
                                  JobLedgEntryRec.RESET;
                                  JobLedgEntryRec.SETCURRENTKEY("Main Project No.","Job No.","Document No.","Posting Date");
                                  IF "Single/Main/Sub Project" <> "Single/Main/Sub Project"::"Main Project" THEN
                                    JobLedgEntryRec.SETFILTER("Job No.","No.");
                                  JobLedgEntryRec.SETFILTER("Main Project No.", "Main Project");
                                  JobLedgEntryRec.SETFILTER("Posting Date",GETFILTER("Cumulation Filter"));
                                  JobLedgEntryRec.SETRANGE("Entry Type",JobLedgEntryRec."Entry Type"::Sale);
                                  JobLedgEntryRec.SETRANGE(Surcharge,FALSE); // Melding C-019331
                                  JobLedgEntryRec.DPA_SetFilters(CurrReport.OBJECTID(FALSE)); //**4PS.n
                                  IF JobLedgEntryRec.FINDSET THEN BEGIN
                                    REPEAT
                                      CustEntryRec.RESET;
                                      CustEntryRec.SETCURRENTKEY("Document No.");
                                      CustEntryRec.SETFILTER(
                                        "Document Type",'%1|%2',CustEntryRec."Document Type"::Invoice,CustEntryRec."Document Type"::"Credit Memo");
                                      CustEntryRec.SETFILTER("Document No.", JobLedgEntryRec."Document No.");
                                      CustEntryRec.SETRANGE("Posting Date", JobLedgEntryRec."Posting Date");
                                      IF CustEntryRec.FINDSET THEN BEGIN
                                        REPEAT
                                          CustEntryRec.CALCFIELDS("Original Amt. (LCY)","Remaining Amt. (LCY)");
                                          PayedAmnt := CustEntryRec."Original Amt. (LCY)" - CustEntryRec."Remaining Amt. (LCY)";
                                          IF CustEntryRec."Remaining Amt. (LCY)" <> 0 THEN
                                            PayedPerc := (PayedAmnt / CustEntryRec."Original Amt. (LCY)") * 100
                                          ELSE
                                            PayedPerc := 100;
                                          CustBalance[1] := CustBalance[1] + (JobLedgEntryRec."Total Price (LCY)" / 100) * PayedPerc;      //Betaalde deb
                                          CustBalance[2] := CustBalance[2] + ((JobLedgEntryRec."Total Price (LCY)" * (100 - PayedPerc))) / 100 ;
                                        UNTIL CustEntryRec.NEXT = 0;
                                      END;
                                    UNTIL JobLedgEntryRec.NEXT = 0;
                                  END;
                                END;

               ReqFilterFields=No. }

    { 1000000002;1;Column;FORMAT_TODAY_0_4___________FORMAT_TIME_;
               SourceExpr=FORMAT(TODAY,0,4) + ' - '+ FORMAT(TIME) }

    { 1000000003;1;Column;COMPANYNAME        ;
               SourceExpr=COMPANYNAME }

    { 1000000004;1;Column;CurrReport_PAGENO  ;
               SourceExpr=CurrReport.PAGENO }

    { 1000000006;1;Column;USERID             ;
               SourceExpr=USERID }

    { 1000000008;1;Column;Job__No__          ;
               SourceExpr="No." }

    { 1000000011;1;Column;Job_Description    ;
               SourceExpr=Description }

    { 1000000014;1;Column;Job__Principal_Name_;
               SourceExpr="Principal Name" }

    { 1000000017;1;Column;Job__Name_Project_Manager_;
               SourceExpr="Name Project Manager" }

    { 1000000016;1;Column;FORMAT_RuwDetailLabel_1__;
               SourceExpr=FORMAT(RuwDetailLabel[1]) }

    { 1000000429;1;Column;Job_GETFILTERS     ;
               SourceExpr=Job.GETFILTERS }

    { 1000000023;1;Column;PrognDate_1_       ;
               SourceExpr=PrognDate[1] }

    { 1000000152;1;Column;PrognDate_2_       ;
               SourceExpr=PrognDate[2] }

    { 68  ;1   ;Column  ;PrognDate_3_        ;
               SourceExpr=PrognDate[3] }

    { 1000000103;1;Column;ProjSrtTxt         ;
               SourceExpr=ProjSrtTxt }

    { 1000000219;1;Column;ToRecSpentDec_4_   ;
               DecimalPlaces=1:1;
               SourceExpr=ToRecSpentDec[4] }

    { 1000000220;1;Column;ROUND_ToRecSpentDec_3__1_;
               DecimalPlaces=0:0;
               SourceExpr=ROUND(ToRecSpentDec[3],1) }

    { 1000000221;1;Column;PercSign           ;
               DecimalPlaces=1:1;
               SourceExpr=PercSign }

    { 1000000047;1;Column;ROUND_PrognTotRevDec_1__1_;
               DecimalPlaces=0:0;
               SourceExpr=ROUND(PrognTotRevDec[1],1) }

    { 1000000065;1;Column;ROUND_PrognTotRevDec_2__1_;
               DecimalPlaces=0:0;
               SourceExpr=ROUND(PrognTotRevDec[2],1) }

    { 1000000244;1;Column;ROUND_PrognTotRevDec_3__1_;
               DecimalPlaces=0:0;
               SourceExpr=ROUND(PrognTotRevDec[3],1) }

    { 1000000254;1;Column;ROUND_PrognTotRevDec_1_____ContractAmount___ExtensionApproved_1____ExtensionApproved_2___1_;
               DecimalPlaces=0:0;
               SourceExpr=ROUND(PrognTotRevDec[1] - (ContractAmount + ExtensionApproved[1] + ExtensionApproved[2]),1) }

    { 1000000105;1;Column;ROUND_InstallmentsInvoiced___ExtensionsInvoiced___CostPlusInvoiced_1_;
               DecimalPlaces=0:0;
               SourceExpr=ROUND(InstallmentsInvoiced + ExtensionsInvoiced + CostPlusInvoiced,1) }

    { 1000000097;1;Column;ROUND_CostPlusInvoiced_1_;
               DecimalPlaces=0:0;
               SourceExpr=ROUND(CostPlusInvoiced,1) }

    { 1000000104;1;Column;ROUND_InstallmentsInvoiced___ExtensionsInvoiced__1_;
               DecimalPlaces=0:0;
               SourceExpr=ROUND(InstallmentsInvoiced + ExtensionsInvoiced ,1) }

    { 1000000102;1;Column;ROUND_ContractAmount___ExtensionApproved_1____ExtensionApproved_2__1_;
               DecimalPlaces=0:0;
               SourceExpr=ROUND(ContractAmount + ExtensionApproved[1] + ExtensionApproved[2],1) }

    { 1000000164;1;Column;ROUND_ExtensionApproved_2__1_;
               DecimalPlaces=0:0;
               SourceExpr=ROUND(ExtensionApproved[2],1) }

    { 1000000101;1;Column;ROUND_ExtensionApproved_1__1_;
               DecimalPlaces=0:0;
               SourceExpr=ROUND(ExtensionApproved[1],1) }

    { 1000000100;1;Column;ROUND_ContractAmount_1_;
               DecimalPlaces=0:0;
               SourceExpr=ROUND(ContractAmount,1) }

    { 1000000107;1;Column;FORMAT_RuwDetailLabel_3__;
               OptionCaptionML=ENU=Detailed,,Rough,Detailed-Rough;
               OptionString=Detailed,,Rough,Detailed-Rough;
               SourceExpr=FORMAT(RuwDetailLabel[3]) }

    { 1000000108;1;Column;FORMAT_RuwDetailLabel_2__;
               OptionCaptionML=ENU=Detailed,,Rough,Detailed-Rough;
               OptionString=Detailed,,Rough,Detailed-Rough;
               SourceExpr=FORMAT(RuwDetailLabel[2]) }

    { 1000000109;1;Column;FORMAT_RuwDetailLabel_1___Control1000000109;
               OptionCaptionML=ENU=Detailed,,Rough,Detailed-Rough;
               OptionString=Detailed,,Rough,Detailed-Rough;
               SourceExpr=FORMAT(RuwDetailLabel[1]) }

    { 1000000187;1;Column;CommentText_4_     ;
               DecimalPlaces=0:0;
               SourceExpr=CommentText[4] }

    { 1000000309;1;Column;CommentText_5_     ;
               DecimalPlaces=0:0;
               SourceExpr=CommentText[5] }

    { 1000000316;1;Column;CommentText_3_     ;
               DecimalPlaces=0:0;
               SourceExpr=CommentText[3] }

    { 1000000330;1;Column;CommentText_2_     ;
               DecimalPlaces=0:0;
               SourceExpr=CommentText[2] }

    { 1000000331;1;Column;CommentText_1_     ;
               DecimalPlaces=0:0;
               SourceExpr=CommentText[1] }

    { 1000000334;1;Column;ROUND__CustBalance_2__1_;
               DecimalPlaces=0:0;
               SourceExpr=ROUND(-CustBalance[2],1) }

    { 1000000335;1;Column;ROUND_VendorBalance_2__1_;
               DecimalPlaces=0:0;
               SourceExpr=ROUND(VendorBalance[2],1) }

    { 1000000347;1;Column;ProgressDec_2_     ;
               DecimalPlaces=1:1;
               SourceExpr=ProgressDec[2] }

    { 1000000348;1;Column;ProgressDec_3_     ;
               DecimalPlaces=1:1;
               SourceExpr=ProgressDec[3] }

    { 1000000349;1;Column;ProgressDec_4_     ;
               DecimalPlaces=1:1;
               SourceExpr=ProgressDec[4] }

    { 1000000350;1;Column;ProgressDec_5_     ;
               DecimalPlaces=1:1;
               SourceExpr=ProgressDec[5] }

    { 1000000351;1;Column;ProgressDec_6_     ;
               DecimalPlaces=1:1;
               SourceExpr=ProgressDec[6] }

    { 1000000359;1;Column;ROUND__InstallmentsInvoiced___ExtensionsInvoiced___CostPlusInvoiced_____Actual_Costs__1_;
               DecimalPlaces=0:0;
               SourceExpr=ROUND((InstallmentsInvoiced + ExtensionsInvoiced + CostPlusInvoiced) - "Actual Costs",1) }

    { 1000000362;1;Column;ROUND_VendorBalance_1__1_;
               DecimalPlaces=0:0;
               SourceExpr=ROUND(VendorBalance[1],1) }

    { 1000000363;1;Column;ROUND__CustBalance_1__1_;
               DecimalPlaces=0:0;
               SourceExpr=ROUND(-CustBalance[1],1) }

    { 1000000365;1;Column;ROUND__CustBalance_1____VendorBalance_1__1_;
               DecimalPlaces=0:0;
               SourceExpr=ROUND(-CustBalance[1] - VendorBalance[1],1) }

    { 1000000368;1;Column;ProgressDec_1_     ;
               DecimalPlaces=1:1;
               SourceExpr=ProgressDec[1] }

    { 1000000371;1;Column;ROUND__Actual_Costs__1_;
               DecimalPlaces=0:0;
               SourceExpr=ROUND("Actual Costs",1) }

    { 1000000372;1;Column;ProjectDays_1__7   ;
               DecimalPlaces=0:0;
               SourceExpr=ProjectDays[1]/7 }

    { 1000000373;1;Column;Job_Job__Ending_Date_;
               SourceExpr=Job."Ending Date" }

    { 1000000374;1;Column;ProjectDays_2__7   ;
               DecimalPlaces=0:0;
               SourceExpr=ProjectDays[2]/7 }

    { 1000000375;1;Column;ProjectDays_3_     ;
               DecimalPlaces=0:0;
               SourceExpr=ProjectDays[3] }

    { 1000000379;1;Column;Job_Job__Starting_Date_;
               SourceExpr=Job."Starting Date" }

    { 1000000386;1;Column;ROUND_InstallmentsInvoiced___ExtensionsInvoiced___CostPlusInvoiced_1__Control1000000386;
               DecimalPlaces=0:0;
               SourceExpr=ROUND(InstallmentsInvoiced + ExtensionsInvoiced + CostPlusInvoiced,1) }

    { 1000000396;1;Column;ROUND_ContractAmount_1__Control1000000396;
               DecimalPlaces=0:0;
               SourceExpr=ROUND(ContractAmount,1) }

    { 1000000397;1;Column;ROUND_InstallmentsInvoiced_1_;
               DecimalPlaces=0:0;
               SourceExpr=ROUND(InstallmentsInvoiced,1) }

    { 1000000398;1;Column;ROUND_ExtensionsInvoiced_1_;
               DecimalPlaces=0:0;
               SourceExpr=ROUND(ExtensionsInvoiced,1) }

    { 1000000401;1;Column;ROUND_ContractAmount___ExtensionApproved_3____ExtensionApproved_4__1_;
               DecimalPlaces=0:0;
               SourceExpr=ROUND(ContractAmount + ExtensionApproved[3] + ExtensionApproved[4],1) }

    { 1000000402;1;Column;ROUND_ExtensionApproved_3__1_;
               DecimalPlaces=0:0;
               SourceExpr=ROUND(ExtensionApproved[3],1) }

    { 1000000403;1;Column;ROUND_ExtensionApproved_4__1_;
               DecimalPlaces=0:0;
               SourceExpr=ROUND(ExtensionApproved[4],1) }

    { 1000000404;1;Column;ROUND_CostPlusInvoiced_1__Control1000000404;
               DecimalPlaces=0:0;
               SourceExpr=ROUND(CostPlusInvoiced,1) }

    { 1000000405;1;Column;ROUND_InstallmentsInvoiced___ExtensionsInvoiced___CostPlusInvoiced_1__Control1000000405;
               DecimalPlaces=0:0;
               SourceExpr=ROUND(InstallmentsInvoiced + ExtensionsInvoiced + CostPlusInvoiced,1) }

    { 1000000406;1;Column;ROUND__ContractAmount___ExtensionApproved_1____ExtensionApproved_2______InstallmentsInvoiced___ExtensionsInvoiced___CostPlusInvoiced__1_;
               DecimalPlaces=0:0;
               SourceExpr=ROUND((ContractAmount + ExtensionApproved[1] + ExtensionApproved[2]) - (InstallmentsInvoiced + ExtensionsInvoiced + CostPlusInvoiced),1) }

    { 1000000407;1;Column;ROUND_ExtensionLikeOrder_1_;
               DecimalPlaces=0:0;
               SourceExpr=ROUND(ExtensionLikeOrder,1) }

    { 1000000408;1;Column;ROUND_ExtensionDec_1__1_;
               DecimalPlaces=0:0;
               SourceExpr=ROUND(ExtensionDec[1],1) }

    { 1000000409;1;Column;ROUND_ExtensionDec_2__1_;
               DecimalPlaces=0:0;
               SourceExpr=ROUND(ExtensionDec[2],1) }

    { 1000000410;1;Column;ROUND_ExtensionLikeOrder___ExtensionDec_1____ExtensionDec_2__1_;
               DecimalPlaces=0:0;
               SourceExpr=ROUND(ExtensionLikeOrder + ExtensionDec[1] + ExtensionDec[2],1) }

    { 1000000411;1;Column;ROUND_ExtensionDec_3__1_;
               DecimalPlaces=0:0;
               SourceExpr=ROUND(ExtensionDec[3],1) }

    { 1210190000;1;Column;PercSign_Control1210190000;
               DecimalPlaces=1:1;
               SourceExpr=PercSign }

    { 1000000020;1;Column;ExpFinishDate      ;
               DecimalPlaces=0:0;
               SourceExpr=ExpFinishDate }

    { 1000000001;1;Column;PCS_TOPsheetCaption;
               SourceExpr=PCS_TOPsheetCaptionLbl }

    { 1000000005;1;Column;CurrReport_PAGENOCaption;
               SourceExpr=CurrReport_PAGENOCaptionLbl }

    { 1000000000;1;Column;Project_Caption    ;
               SourceExpr=Project_CaptionLbl }

    { 1000000007;1;Column;Omschrijving_Caption;
               SourceExpr=Omschrijving_CaptionLbl }

    { 1000000009;1;Column;Opdrachtgever_Caption;
               SourceExpr=Opdrachtgever_CaptionLbl }

    { 1000000010;1;Column;Projectleider_Caption;
               SourceExpr=Projectleider_CaptionLbl }

    { 1000000012;1;Column;Vorige_prognose_datum_Caption;
               SourceExpr=Vorige_prognose_datum_CaptionLbl }

    { 1000000013;1;Column;Prognose_datum_Caption;
               SourceExpr=Prognose_datum_CaptionLbl }

    { 1000000015;1;Column;Type_prognose_Caption;
               SourceExpr=Type_prognose_CaptionLbl }

               SourceExpr=Enkel_Hoofd_Deelproject_CaptionLbl }

    { 1000000077;1;Column;MutatieCaption     ;
               SourceExpr=MutatieCaptionLbl }

    { 1000000080;1;Column;PrognoseCaption    ;
               SourceExpr=PrognoseCaptionLbl }

    { 1000000078;1;Column;Begr_vs_progCaption;
               SourceExpr=Begr_vs_progCaptionLbl }

    { 1000000079;1;Column;PeriodeCaption     ;
               SourceExpr=PeriodeCaptionLbl }

    { 39  ;1   ;Column  ;PrognosisTypeLabel  ;
               SourceExpr=PrognosisTypeLabel }

    { 8508;1   ;DataItem;Kosten              ;
               DataItemTable=Table11012047;
               DataItemTableView=SORTING(Project No.,Cost Type,Cost Object);
               OnPreDataItem=BEGIN
                               CurrReport.CREATETOTALS("Hours Prognosis","Prognosis Hours Prev Period",TotalCostDec,ToRecSpentDec[1]);//, PrognHoursDec);
                               CurrReport.CREATETOTALS("Received/Not Inv. Hours","Open Amount (Hours)", TotHoursDec);
                               CurrReport.CREATETOTALS("Open Ovh. Surch. Soft (Purch.)","Open Ovh. Surch. Firm (Purch.)");
                               TempTotCostDec := 0;
                             END;

               OnAfterGetRecord=BEGIN
                                  SETFILTER("Cumulation Filter", CumulationFilterTxt);
                                  SETFILTER("Period Filter", PeriodFilterTxt);

                                  ClearVarCostObj;
                                  CostCtrlManagement.CalcFieldsCostObj(Kosten);
                                  TotalCostDec := CostCtrlManagement.TotCostCostObj(Kosten,TRUE);
                                  TotHoursDec := CostCtrlManagement.TotHoursCostObj(Kosten,TRUE);

                                  LineNumber += 10000;
                                  Prognose1 := 0 ;
                                  Prognose2 := 0 ;
                                  Prognose3 := 0 ;
                                  Prognose1_Arbeid := 0;
                                  Prognose2_Arbeid := 0;
                                  Prognose3_Arbeid := 0;
                                  IF STRSUBSTNO('%1',"Cost Type") <> prevCostType THEN BEGIN
                                    prevCostType := STRSUBSTNO('%1',Kosten."Cost Type");
                                    LineNumberCostType := 0;
                                    Prognose1 := ROUND(PrognTotCostDec[1,"Cost Type"+1],1);
                                    Prognose2 := ROUND(PrognTotCostDec[2,"Cost Type"+1],1);
                                    Prognose3 := ROUND(PrognTotCostDec[3,"Cost Type"+1],1);
                                    GETLaborTotals;
                                  END;
                                  LineNumberCostType +=10000;

                                  IF PrognTotCostDec[1,7] <> 0 THEN
                                    ProgressDec[6] := (TotalCostDec / PrognTotCostDec[1,7]) ;

                                  //Marge %
                                  IF ContractAmount <> 0 THEN
                                    MargePerc[11] := ROUND(((ContractAmount - "Original Budget Amount") / ContractAmount) , 0.1);
                                  IF (ContractAmount + ExtensionApproved[1] + ExtensionApproved[2]) <> 0 THEN
                                    MargePerc[12] := ROUND((((ContractAmount + ExtensionApproved[1] + ExtensionApproved[2]) - Budget) /
                                      (ContractAmount + ExtensionApproved[1] + ExtensionApproved[2])) , 0.1);
                                  IF (InstallmentsInvoiced + ExtensionsInvoiced + CostPlusInvoiced) <> 0 THEN
                                    MargePerc[13] := ROUND((((InstallmentsInvoiced + ExtensionsInvoiced + CostPlusInvoiced) - TotalCostDec) /
                                      (InstallmentsInvoiced + ExtensionsInvoiced + CostPlusInvoiced)) , 0.1);
                                  IF ToRecSpentDec[3] <> 0 THEN
                                    MargePerc[14] := ROUND(((ToRecSpentDec[3] - ToRecSpentDec[1]) / ToRecSpentDec[3]) , 0.1);
                                  IF PrognTotRevDec[3] <> 0 THEN
                                    MargePerc[15] := ROUND((PrognTotRevDec[3] - PrognTotCostDec[3,7]) / PrognTotRevDec[3] , 0.1);
                                  IF PrognTotRevDec[2] <> 0 THEN
                                    MargePerc[16] := ROUND((PrognTotRevDec[2] - PrognTotCostDec[2,7]) / PrognTotRevDec[2] , 0.1);
                                  IF PrognTotRevDec[1] <> 0 THEN
                                    MargePerc[17] := ROUND((PrognTotRevDec[1] - PrognTotCostDec[1,7]) / PrognTotRevDec[1] , 0.1);

                                  //Markup %
                                  IF "Original Budget Amount" <> 0 THEN
                                    MargePerc[1] := ROUND(((ContractAmount - "Original Budget Amount") / "Original Budget Amount") , 0.1);
                                  IF Budget <> 0 THEN
                                    MargePerc[4] := ROUND((((ContractAmount + ExtensionApproved[1] + ExtensionApproved[2]) - Budget) /
                                      Budget) , 0.1);
                                  IF ("Actual Costs" + TotalCostDec) <> 0 THEN
                                    MargePerc[5] := ROUND((((InstallmentsInvoiced + ExtensionsInvoiced + CostPlusInvoiced) - TotalCostDec) /
                                      TotalCostDec) , 0.1);
                                  IF ToRecSpentDec[1] <> 0 THEN
                                    MargePerc[6] := ROUND(((ToRecSpentDec[3] - ToRecSpentDec[1]) / ToRecSpentDec[1]) , 0.1);
                                  IF PrognTotCostDec[3,7] <> 0 THEN
                                    MargePerc[7] := ROUND((PrognTotRevDec[3] - PrognTotCostDec[3,7]) / PrognTotCostDec[3,7] , 0.1);
                                  IF PrognTotCostDec[2,7] <> 0 THEN
                                    MargePerc[8] := ROUND((PrognTotRevDec[2] - PrognTotCostDec[2,7]) / PrognTotCostDec[2,7] , 0.1);
                                  IF PrognTotCostDec[1,7] <> 0 THEN
                                    MargePerc[9] := ROUND((PrognTotRevDec[1] - PrognTotCostDec[1,7]) / PrognTotCostDec[1,7] , 0.1);

                                  IF Budget <> 0 THEN
                                    ToRecSpentDec[2] := ToRecSpentDec[1] / Budget ;


                                  VerplDec := ROUND("Open (Purchase)" + "Received/Not Invoiced" + "Open Ovh. Surch. Soft (Purch.)" +
                                   "Open Ovh. Surch. Firm (Purch.)" + "Open Amount (Hours)" + "Open Ovh. Surch. (Hours)" +
                                   "Open (Inventory)" + "Open Ovh. Surch. (Inventory)" + "Risc Coverage (Prognosis)",1);
                                END;

               DataItemLink=Project No.=FIELD(No.) }

  {
    PROPERTIES
    {
      OnInit=BEGIN
               IF Job.GETFILTER("Period Filter") <> '' THEN
                 PeriodFilterTxt := Job.GETFILTER("Period Filter");
             END;

      OnOpenPage=BEGIN
                   IF Job.GETFILTER("Period Filter") <> '' THEN
                     PeriodFilterTxt := Job.GETFILTER("Period Filter");
                 END;

    }
    CONTROLS
    {
      { 1100409000;;Container;
                  Name=test;
                  ContainerType=ContentArea }

      { 1100409001;1;Group  ;
                  GroupType=Group }

      { 1100409002;2;Field  ;
                  CaptionML=ENU=Period Filter;
                  SourceExpr=PeriodFilterTxt;
                  OnLookup=VAR
                             DateSelectionManagement@1100409000 : Codeunit 11130005;
                           BEGIN
                             DateSelectionManagement.GetPeriod(PeriodFilterTxt);
                             Text := PeriodFilterTxt;
                           END;
                            }

    }

    PROCEDURE ClearVarCostObj@1000000029();
    BEGIN
      ToRecSpentDec[1] := 0;
      CLEAR(EstimateDec);
      CLEAR(EstimateHoursDec);
      CLEAR(TotalCostDec);
    END;

    PROCEDURE ClearVarJob@1000000000();
    BEGIN
      CLEAR(ContractAmount);
      CLEAR(ProjectDays);
      CLEAR(ExtensionsInvoiced);
      CLEAR(InstallmentsInvoiced);
      CLEAR(CostPlusInvoiced);
      CLEAR(ExtensionApproved);
      CLEAR(ExtensionLikeOrder);
      CLEAR(ExtensionDec);
      CLEAR(ProgressDec);
      CLEAR(CommentText);
      CLEAR(MargePerc);
      CLEAR(VendorBalance);
      CLEAR(PayedAmnt);
      CLEAR(PayedPerc);
      CLEAR(CustBalance);
      CLEAR(PrognTotRevDec);
      CLEAR(PrognTotCostDec);
      CLEAR(AverageRateDec);
      CLEAR(PrognHoursDec);
      //CLEAR(BudgetvsProgn);
      CLEAR(ToRecSpentDec);
      CLEAR(TotHoursDec);
      CLEAR(ExpFinishDate);
      CLEAR(FoundRoughProgn);
      CLEAR(FoundDetProgn);
      CLEAR(PrognDate);
      CLEAR(ProjSrtTxt);
      CLEAR(EstimateTotalDec);
    END;

    PROCEDURE CreateCommentLine@1000000023(pJobNo@1000000000 : Code[20]);
    VAR
      lvCommentLine@1000000001 : Record 97;
      lvInt@1000000002 : Integer;
    BEGIN
      WITH lvCommentLine DO BEGIN
        SETCURRENTKEY("Table Name","No.","Comment Code",Date);
        SETRANGE("Table Name", lvCommentLine."Table Name"::Job);
        SETRANGE("No.", pJobNo);
        ASCENDING(TRUE);
        IF FINDSET THEN BEGIN
          lvInt := 5;
          REPEAT
            CommentText[lvInt] := STRSUBSTNO('%1: %2',Date,Comment);
            lvInt := lvInt - 1;
          UNTIL (NEXT = 0) OR (lvInt = 0);
        END;
      END;
    END;

    PROCEDURE SearchPrognosis@1000000001(pPeriod@1000000004 : Integer;pCumFilter@1000000002 : Text[30];pProjectLevel@1210190000 : 'Single,Main Project,Sub Project');
    VAR
      lvJob@1210190002 : Record 11072003;
      lvPrognosis@1210190001 : Record 11012034;
      lvPrognosisLine@1210190003 : Record 11012035;
      i@1000000000 : Integer;
    BEGIN
      //PrognTotCostDec
      //1 = Labor
      //2 = Material
      //3 = Subcontracting
      //4 = Plant
      //5 = Sundry
      //6 = Revenue
      //7 = Total

      IF pProjectLevel = pProjectLevel::"Main Project" THEN BEGIN
        lvJob.RESET;
        lvJob.SETCURRENTKEY("Main Project");
        lvJob.SETRANGE("Main Project", Job."No.");
        IF lvJob.FINDFIRST THEN
          REPEAT
            lvPrognosis.RESET;
            lvPrognosis.SETRANGE("Project No.", lvJob."No.");
            lvPrognosis.SETFILTER("Prognosis Date", pCumFilter);
            IF lvPrognosis.FINDLAST THEN BEGIN
              PrognDate[pPeriod] := lvPrognosis."Prognosis Date";
              IF lvPrognosis."Expected Finishing Date" > ExpFinishDate THEN
                ExpFinishDate := lvPrognosis."Expected Finishing Date";
              IF lvPrognosis."Prognosis Level" = lvPrognosis."Prognosis Level"::Rough THEN BEGIN
                FoundRoughProgn[pPeriod] := TRUE;
                PrognTotRevDec[pPeriod] += lvPrognosis."Rough Prognosis Total Revenues";
                PrognTotCostDec[pPeriod,7] += lvPrognosis."Rough Prognosis Total Cost";
              END ELSE BEGIN
                lvPrognosis.CALCFIELDS("Prognosis Revenue");
                PrognTotRevDec[pPeriod] += lvPrognosis."Prognosis Revenue" + lvPrognosis."Project Invoiced";
                lvPrognosisLine.RESET;
                lvPrognosisLine.SETRANGE("Project No.", lvPrognosis."Project No.");
                lvPrognosisLine.SETRANGE("Prognosis Date", lvPrognosis."Prognosis Date");
                IF lvPrognosisLine.FINDFIRST THEN
                  FoundDetProgn[pPeriod] := TRUE;
                  REPEAT
                    PrognTotCostDec[pPeriod,lvPrognosisLine."Cost Type" + 1] += lvPrognosisLine."Prognosis Total Cost";
                    PrognTotCostDec[pPeriod,7] += lvPrognosisLine."Prognosis Total Cost";
                  UNTIL lvPrognosisLine.NEXT = 0;
              END;
            END;
          UNTIL lvJob.NEXT = 0;
      END ELSE BEGIN
        lvPrognosis.RESET;
        lvPrognosis.SETRANGE("Project No.", Job."No.");
        lvPrognosis.SETFILTER("Prognosis Date", pCumFilter);
        IF lvPrognosis.FINDLAST THEN BEGIN
          PrognDate[pPeriod] := lvPrognosis."Prognosis Date";
          IF lvPrognosis."Expected Finishing Date" > ExpFinishDate THEN
            ExpFinishDate := lvPrognosis."Expected Finishing Date";
          IF lvPrognosis."Prognosis Level" = lvPrognosis."Prognosis Level"::Rough THEN BEGIN
            FoundRoughProgn[pPeriod] := TRUE;
            PrognTotRevDec[pPeriod] += lvPrognosis."Rough Prognosis Total Revenues";
            PrognTotCostDec[pPeriod,7] += lvPrognosis."Rough Prognosis Total Cost";
          END ELSE BEGIN
            lvPrognosis.CALCFIELDS("Prognosis Revenue");
            PrognTotRevDec[pPeriod] += lvPrognosis."Prognosis Revenue" + lvPrognosis."Project Invoiced";
            lvPrognosisLine.RESET;
            lvPrognosisLine.SETRANGE("Project No.", lvPrognosis."Project No.");
            lvPrognosisLine.SETRANGE("Prognosis Date", lvPrognosis."Prognosis Date");
            IF lvPrognosisLine.FINDFIRST THEN
              FoundDetProgn[pPeriod] := TRUE;
              REPEAT
            //      lvPrognosisLine.CALCFIELDS("Prognosis Total Hours");
                  PrognTotCostDec[pPeriod,lvPrognosisLine."Cost Type" + 1] += lvPrognosisLine."Prognosis Total Cost";
                  PrognTotCostDec[pPeriod,7] += lvPrognosisLine."Prognosis Total Cost";
                  IF lvPrognosisLine."Cost Type" = lvPrognosisLine."Cost Type"::Labor THEN
                    PrognHoursDec[pPeriod] += lvPrognosisLine."Prognosis Total Hours";//test
              UNTIL lvPrognosisLine.NEXT = 0;
          END;
        END;
      END;

      IF (FoundRoughProgn[pPeriod]) AND (NOT FoundDetProgn[pPeriod]) THEN
        PrognosisTypeLabel := RuwLbl;

      IF (NOT FoundRoughProgn[pPeriod]) AND (FoundDetProgn[pPeriod]) THEN
       PrognosisTypeLabel := Gedetailleerdlbl;

      IF (FoundRoughProgn[pPeriod]) AND (FoundDetProgn[pPeriod]) THEN BEGIN
        PrognosisTypeLabel := RuwGedetailleerdlbl;
        FOR i := 1 TO 6 DO BEGIN
          PrognTotCostDec[pPeriod, i] := 0;
        END;
      END;
    END;

    PROCEDURE SearchPeriods@1000000010();
    VAR
      lvPeriodFilterTxt@1000000003 : Text[30];
      lvCumulationFilterTxt@1000000002 : Text[30];
      lvDatFilterStart@1000000001 : Date;
      lvDatFilterEnd@1000000000 : Date;
    BEGIN
      lvDatFilterStart := DatFilterStart;
      lvDatFilterEnd := DatFilterEnd;
      lvCumulationFilterTxt := CumulationFilterTxt;
      lvPeriodFilterTxt := PeriodFilterTxt;
      SearchPeriod.FindPeriod(lvDatFilterStart,lvDatFilterEnd,lvCumulationFilterTxt,lvPeriodFilterTxt,PeriodType,'=');
      PeriodDate[1] := lvCumulationFilterTxt;//Job.GETFILTER("Period Filter");
      SearchPeriod.FindPeriod(lvDatFilterStart,lvDatFilterEnd,lvCumulationFilterTxt,lvPeriodFilterTxt,PeriodType,'<=');
      PeriodDate[2] := lvCumulationFilterTxt;//lvPeriodFilterTxt;

      SearchPeriod.FindPeriod(lvDatFilterStart,lvDatFilterEnd,lvCumulationFilterTxt,lvPeriodFilterTxt,PeriodType,'<=');
      PeriodDate[3] := lvCumulationFilterTxt;//lvPeriodFilterTxt;
    END;

    PROCEDURE GETLaborTotals@21();
    VAR
      cpcorec@1000 : Record 11012047;
      lvJobRec@1001 : Record 11072003;
      lvDatFilterStart@1002 : Date;
      lvDatFilterEnd@1003 : Date;
      lvCumulationFilterTxt@1004 : Text[100];
      lvPeriodFilterTxt@1005 : Text[100];
    BEGIN
      cpcorec.RESET;
      cpcorec.SETCURRENTKEY("Project No.","Cost Type","Cost Object");
      cpcorec.SETRANGE("Project No.",Job."No.");
      cpcorec.SETRANGE(cpcorec."Cost Type",Kosten."Cost Type");

      cpcorec.SETFILTER("Cumulation Filter", CumulationFilterTxt);
      cpcorec.SETFILTER("Period Filter", PeriodFilterTxt);

      //SearchPrognosis(1,PeriodDate[1],Job."Single/Main/Sub Project");
      //SearchPrognosis(2,PeriodDate[2],Job."Single/Main/Sub Project");
      //SearchPrognosis(3,PeriodDate[3],Job."Single/Main/Sub Project");


      IF cpcorec.FINDSET THEN BEGIN
         TempTotCostDec := 0 ;
        REPEAT
          cpcorec.CALCFIELDS("Original Budget Amount","Original Budget Hours",Adjustments,"Adjustments Hours",Extension,"Extension Hours",
                             "Actual Hours",Budget,"Budget Hours","Actual Costs","Received/Not Invoiced","Open Ovh. Surch. Firm (Purch.)" ,
                             "Open Amount (Hours)","Open Ovh. Surch. (Hours)","Open (Inventory)","Open Ovh. Surch. (Inventory)","Risc Coverage (Prognosis)");
       //   IF cpcorec."Cost Type" = cpcorec."Cost Type"::Labor THEN BEGIN
            tempdec1 += cpcorec."Original Budget Amount";
            tempdec2 += cpcorec."Original Budget Hours";
            tempdec3 += cpcorec.Adjustments;
            tempdec4 += cpcorec."Adjustments Hours";
            tempdec5 += cpcorec.Extension;
            tempdec6 += cpcorec."Extension Hours";
            tempdec7 += cpcorec.Budget;
            tempdec8 += cpcorec."Budget Hours";
            tempdec9 += cpcorec."Actual Hours";
            tempdec10 += cpcorec."Hours Prognosis";


            TempTotCostDec +=
              cpcorec."Actual Costs" +
              cpcorec."Received/Not Invoiced" + cpcorec."Open Ovh. Surch. Firm (Purch.)" +
              cpcorec."Open Amount (Hours)" + cpcorec."Open Ovh. Surch. (Hours)" +
              cpcorec."Open (Inventory)" + cpcorec."Open Ovh. Surch. (Inventory)" +
              cpcorec."Risc Coverage (Prognosis)";
       //   END;
        UNTIL cpcorec.NEXT = 0;

        cpcorec.SETFILTER("Cumulation Filter", CumulationFilterTxt);
        cpcorec.SETFILTER("Period Filter", PeriodFilterTxt);

        TotHoursDec := tempdec9;

        IF tempdec2 <> 0 THEN
          AverageRateDec[1] := tempdec1 / tempdec2;
        IF tempdec4 <> 0 THEN
          AverageRateDec[2] := tempdec3 / tempdec4;
        IF tempdec6 <> 0 THEN
          AverageRateDec[3] := tempdec5 / tempdec6;
        IF tempdec8 <> 0 THEN
          AverageRateDec[4] := tempdec7 / tempdec8;
        IF tempdec9 <> 0 THEN
          AverageRateDec[5] := TotalCostDec / tempdec9;
        IF EstimateHoursDec <> 0 THEN
          AverageRateDec[9] := EstimateDec / EstimateHoursDec;
        IF (tempdec8 - tempdec9) <> 0 THEN
          AverageRateDec[10] += (tempdec7 - TempTotCostDec) / (tempdec8 - tempdec9);

         IF TotalCostDec <> 0 THEN
           ToRecSpentDec[1] := (tempdec7 - TotalCostDec);
      END;


      IF PrognTotCostDec[1,Kosten."Cost Type"+1] <> 0 THEN BEGIN
        IF Kosten."Cost Type" = Kosten."Cost Type"::Labor THEN
          ProgressDec[Kosten."Cost Type" + 1] := (TempTotCostDec / PrognTotCostDec[1,Kosten."Cost Type"+1]) * 100
        ELSE
           ProgressDec[Kosten."Cost Type" + 1] := (TotalCostDec / PrognTotCostDec[1,Kosten."Cost Type"+1]) * 100;
      END;

      IF Kosten.Budget <> 0 THEN
        ToRecSpentDec[2] := ToRecSpentDec[1] / Kosten.Budget * 100;

                                                                      //TotCostCostObj
      lvJobRec.COPY(Job);
      lvDatFilterStart := DatFilterStart;
      lvDatFilterEnd := DatFilterEnd;
      lvCumulationFilterTxt := CumulationFilterTxt;
      lvPeriodFilterTxt := PeriodFilterTxt;

      IF (PrognDate[1] <> 0D) AND (NOT FoundRoughProgn[1]) THEN BEGIN
        lvDatFilterStart := DatFilterStart;
        lvDatFilterEnd := DatFilterEnd;
        lvCumulationFilterTxt := CumulationFilterTxt;
        lvPeriodFilterTxt := PeriodFilterTxt;
        SearchPeriod.FindPeriod(lvDatFilterStart,lvDatFilterEnd,lvCumulationFilterTxt,lvPeriodFilterTxt,PeriodType,'<');
        lvJobRec.SETFILTER("Cumulation Filter", CumulationFilterTxt);
        lvJobRec.SETFILTER("Period Filter", PeriodFilterTxt);
        lvJobRec.SETFILTER("Prognosis Filter", '%1', PrognDate[1]);
        lvJobRec.SETFILTER("Original Cost Type Filter",'%1',lvJobRec."Original Cost Type Filter"::Labor);
       // PrognHoursDec[1] := CostCtrlManagement.PrognTotHoursProject(lvJobRec,TRUE);
      END ELSE
        PrognHoursDec[1] := 0;

      IF (PrognDate[2] <> 0D) AND (NOT FoundRoughProgn[2]) THEN BEGIN
        SearchPeriod.FindPeriod(lvDatFilterStart,lvDatFilterEnd,lvCumulationFilterTxt,lvPeriodFilterTxt,PeriodType,'<=');
        lvJobRec.SETFILTER("Cumulation Filter", lvCumulationFilterTxt);
        lvJobRec.SETFILTER("Period Filter", lvPeriodFilterTxt);
        lvJobRec.SETFILTER("Prognosis Filter", '%1', PrognDate[2]);
        lvJobRec.SETFILTER("Original Cost Type Filter",'%1',lvJobRec."Original Cost Type Filter"::Labor);
      //  PrognHoursDec[2] := CostCtrlManagement.PrognTotHoursProject(lvJobRec,TRUE);
      END ELSE
        PrognHoursDec[2] := 0;

      IF (PrognDate[3] <> 0D) AND (NOT FoundRoughProgn[3]) THEN BEGIN
        SearchPeriod.FindPeriod(lvDatFilterStart,lvDatFilterEnd,lvCumulationFilterTxt,lvPeriodFilterTxt,PeriodType,'<=');
        lvJobRec.SETFILTER("Cumulation Filter", lvCumulationFilterTxt);
        lvJobRec.SETFILTER("Period Filter", lvPeriodFilterTxt);
        lvJobRec.SETFILTER("Prognosis Filter", '%1', PrognDate[3]);
        lvJobRec.SETFILTER("Original Cost Type Filter",'%1',lvJobRec."Original Cost Type Filter"::Labor);
      //  PrognHoursDec[3] := CostCtrlManagement.PrognTotHoursProject(lvJobRec,TRUE);
      END ELSE
        PrognHoursDec[3] := 0;

      IF PrognHoursDec[1] <> 0 THEN
        AverageRateDec[6] := PrognTotCostDec[1,1] / PrognHoursDec[1];
      IF PrognHoursDec[2] <> 0 THEN
        AverageRateDec[7] := PrognTotCostDec[2,1] / PrognHoursDec[2];
      IF PrognHoursDec[3] <> 0 THEN
        AverageRateDec[8] := PrognTotCostDec[3,1] / PrognHoursDec[3];
    END;

    BEGIN
    {
      MC060513: Besteed werd niet goed berekend bij deelproject: projectfilter toegevoegd en daarna pas calcfields.
      MC060513: Calculatie wordt nu via vervolgtraject opgehaald, bij RAW direct.
      BK081014: Layout overgezet van 2009 naar 2013R2
    }
    END.
  }

  <Code>Public Function BlankZero(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value = 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankPos(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &gt; 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankZeroAndPos(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &gt;= 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankNeg(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &lt; 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankNegAndZero(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &lt;= 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function
</Code>
